---
title: Smart Paneer, Chickpea and Chicken Breasts Curry with Spinach in Tikka Sauce
description: Golden morsels of paneer have a delicate creamy interior while the outer layer is delightfully crispy after getting a quick toss in the pan. Coupled with fibre-rich chickpeas stewed in a creamy tikka sauce, this curry is not to be missed!
